Values.html#Lean.Meta.getBitVecValue?","doc":"Return `some ⟨n, v⟩` if `e` is:\n- an `OfNat.ofNat` application\n- a `BitVec.ofNat` application\n- a `BitVec.ofNatLT` application\nthat encode a `BitVec n` with value `v`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/LitValues.html#Lean.Meta.getBitVecValue?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">getBitVecValue?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">((<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>) × <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BitVec\">BitVec</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>)</span>)</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/LitValues.lean#L69-L75","name":"Lean.Meta.getFinValue?","line":69,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/LitValues.html#Lean.Meta.getFinValue?","doc":"Return `some ⟨n, v⟩` if `e` is an `OfNat.ofNat` application encoding a `Fin n` with value `v` "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/LitValues.html#Lean.Meta.getFinValue?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">getFinValue?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span cla