ue?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a>)</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/LitValues.lean#L49-L55","name":"Lean.Meta.getIntValue?","line":49,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/LitValues.html#Lean.Meta.getIntValue?","doc":"Return `some i` if `e` `OfNat.ofNat`-application encoding an integer, or `Neg.neg`-application of one. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/LitValues.html#Lean.Meta.getIntValue?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">getIntValue?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Data/Int/Basic.html#Int\">Int</a>)</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/LitValues.lean#L41-L47","name":"Lean.Meta.getNatValue?","line":41,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/LitValues.html#Lean.Meta.getNatValue?","doc":"Return `some n` if `e` is a raw natural number or an `OfNat.ofNat`-application encoding `n`. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span 